---
import '../styles/components/professional-approach.css';
---

<section class="approach" id="approach">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="approach__header">
      <h2 class="approach__title" data-animate="fade-up">Professional Approach To Realization Of All Your Great Ideas</h2>
      <p class="approach__subtitle" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="0.2">
        To work with our clients to identify real business opportunities and match up the right technologies in order to create fast and effective applications.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="approach__grid">
      <!-- Website Development -->
      <article class="approach-card" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="0.1">
        <div class="approach-card__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="approach-card__title">WEBSITE DEVELOPMENT</h3>
        <p class="approach-card__description">
          A simple to-go solution for many businesses is developing a responsive web app at the beginning, which will help minimize the cost for update and maintenance in the long run.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Mobile Development -->
      <article class="approach-card" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="0.3">
        <div class="approach-card__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="approach-card__title">MOBILE DEVELOPMENT</h3>
        <p class="approach-card__description">
          Our versatile experience in offshore mobile app development allows us to support our clients and their business regardless of which industry they belong...
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Platform Development -->
      <article class="approach-card" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="0.5">
        <div class="approach-card__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <line x1="22" y1="12" x2="2" y2="12"/>
            <path d="M5.45 5.11L2 12v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-6l-3.45-6.89A2 2 0 0 0 16.76 4H7.24a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11z"/>
            <line x1="6" y1="16" x2="6.01" y2="16"/>
            <line x1="10" y1="16" x2="10.01" y2="16"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="approach-card__title">PLATFORM DEVELOPMENT</h3>
        <p class="approach-card__description">
          Today’s applications are not standalone apps that works only on a PC or a phone. They require integration and connection to the internet, with numerous services and customizations.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
